original_title: When Ant & Dec Met The Prince: 40 Years of The Prince's Trust
overview: In an interview with Ant and Dec, Princes William and Harry have been speaking about their Dad's work with the Prince's Trust charity. It was set up by Prince Charles 40 years ago and has become one of Britain's biggest youth charities and has helped more than 825,000 young people.
title: When Ant & Dec Met The Prince: 40 Years of The Prince's Trust
